response.original_title: A Snake in the Grass (Inspired by The Princess Bride)
response.overview: In a deadly ring built on grass, an experienced duelist faces a mysterious newcomer. What begins as a fight for survival becomes a confrontation with hidden truths. Inspired by the iconic duel from The Princess Bride.
response.tagline: Hello. My name is Willem van Renswoudt.
